Daimler Expects Majority Stake in Tognum, Handelsblatt Reports

-- B y   C h r i s t i a n   V i t s
-- 
2011-06-05T17:35:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-05/daimler-expects-majority-stake-in-tognum-handelsblatt-reports.html
Daimler AG (DAI)  and Rolls-Royce Holdings
Plc expect to achieve a “clear majority” stake in German
engine-maker  Tognum AG (TGM) ,  Handelsblatt  reported, citing an
interview with Daimler’s Chief Financial Officer Bodo Uebber.  While the term of acceptance for the takeover offer ended
on June 2, investors have a chance for late registration to
accept the bid until June 20, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Christian Vits in Frankfurt at 
 cvits@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Craig Stirling at   cstirling1@bloomberg.net  